      <title>Starboard Value 斥资 10 亿美元入股辉瑞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/starboard-value-take-1-billion-stake-in-pfizer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，激进投资者 Starboard Value 正寻求推动辉瑞公司扭亏为盈，将收购这家陷入困境的制药巨头约 10 亿美元的股份。查理·韦尔斯在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/starboard-value-take-1-billion-stake-in-pfizer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 10:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特在英国败诉，因伦敦金属交易所关闭镍市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elliott-loses-uk-appeal-over-lme-s-nickel-market-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于伦敦金属交易所 (London Metal Exchange) 做出了有争议的决定，阻止镍市场失控的空头挤压，埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 在英国失去了吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elliott-loses-uk-appeal-over-lme-s-nickel-market-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:44:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德：即使没有中国刺激措施，矿业股看起来也很便宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/blackrock-miners-look-cheap-even-without-china-stimulus-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德基本股票主题和行业投资主管埃维·汉布罗 (Evy Hambro) 讨论了采矿业及其相关大宗商品的前景。“我们对股票前景持乐观态度，”他告诉彭博电视台。“如果我们确实在紧张的市场中看到一些额外需求，那将推高价格。如果它推高了价格，那么盈利能力将进一步提高，”汉布罗说。他还讨论了“动物精神”和并购，此前力拓集团于周一对 Arcadium Lithium Plc 进行了收购。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/blackrock-miners-look-cheap-even-without-china-stimulus-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁索洛兹将儿子逐出波兰公用事业公司董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/billionaire-solorz-ousts-sons-from-polish-utility-s-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰亿万富翁齐格蒙特·索洛兹 (Zygmunt Solorz) 将他的两个儿子从公用事业公司 ZE PAK SA 的监事会中赶了出去，加深了家族对其企业集团控制权的争夺，该集团还包括媒体和电信行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/billionaire-solorz-ousts-sons-from-polish-utility-s-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙以 65 亿美元出售加拿大油砂、页岩资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chevron-sells-oil-sands-and-shale-assets-to-cnr-for-6-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司同意以 65 亿美元的价格将其持有的部分油砂和页岩资产的股份出售给加拿大自然资源有限公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chevron-sells-oil-sands-and-shale-assets-to-cnr-for-6-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新考虑政策，关键美国债券收益率自 8 月以来首次触及 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份强劲的就业报告迫使交易员重新评估货币政策前景后，美国主要国债收益率回升至 4%，为 8 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
