    <item>
      <title>铁矿石价格上涨，因预期中国将推出更多刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/iron-ore-pushes-higher-on-hopes-more-china-stimulus-is-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格上涨——延续两周的大幅上涨——因市场猜测中国最高经济规划者将于周二推出更多刺激措施。其他工业金属价格基本保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/iron-ore-pushes-higher-on-hopes-more-china-stimulus-is-coming</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：利率下行押注减弱推高债券收益率，股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强劲的美国经济数据迫使交易员减少对美联储今年可能降息幅度的押注，股市下跌，债券收益率延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风米尔顿横扫墨西哥湾，直逼佛罗里达州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/florida-faces-deadly-tropical-threat-in-hurricane-helene-s-wake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风米尔顿正向佛罗里达州前进，强度可能达到 4 级，并可能引发七年来最大规模的撤离，因为它的目标是该州的墨西哥湾沿岸和坦帕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/florida-faces-deadly-tropical-threat-in-hurricane-helene-s-wake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
